{"tid":1333260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求各位幫手做義工助選","createTime":"2019-07-19T15:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T03:44:49.000Z","uid":241066,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e52644d6663ef295468a17666452d7bb0cb2e8b","tid":1333260,"uid":241066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:28:08.000Z","msg":"有冇人想幫油塘區嘅參選人做義工（文宣，街站果d都要）？ 而家人手好緊， <a href=\"http://有ge請入t.me/YauTong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9C%89ge%E8%AB%8B%E5%85%A5t.me%2FYauTong&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=7e806363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">有ge請入t.me/YauTong</a><br />\n點解建制派區選會比非建制派有利？因為人數差距，因此建制派有強勁ge組織票。根據現任順天邨區議員莫建成係2015年ge訪問：對手以近20：1ge助選團強攻。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因此，我地好需要各位ge支持去打呢場選戰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n介紹下積極人士ricky先：居住油塘二十多年，無從政經驗。<br />\n<br />\n傘後起痛恨政府，經過反送中運動，啟發於「各有各做」，好認同每個人都要喺自己崗位做點事為香港，捍衛民主自由<br />\n<br />\n投奔社會工作超過五年，事業開始起步搵到自己既位置，開始可以分配更多時間。雖然自知自己準備近乎零，但佢有既係心，放膽一試。<br />\n<br />\n佢係一個溫和，唔鍾意嘈交既人，油塘東好多年長既選民，佢會比較以尊重方式對待不喜歡佢既人。雖然如此，但有見油塘連濃牆事件揭發，油塘有好多深藍絲，再加上鄰近紀律部隊宿舍，街站可能有一定危險性，所以街站方面每次至少要兩個人。<br />\n<br />\n係呢度多謝各位肯幫我地ge義工"},{"pid":"0dfc17fc91ec106a30100e96ba38302d277e188c","tid":1333260,"uid":241066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:28:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/YauTong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FYauTong&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J4VlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=6efcc9d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/YauTong</a>"},{"pid":"7ccc6dfc5c68e6facf41687c027330cb4a371cfc","tid":1333260,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c57d74f23f60e77c3cfdff1453bbe3b72c2908a","tid":1333260,"uid":241066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:39:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c66bad5ca1bae4869281cace345e78b817122bb1","tid":1333260,"uid":241066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"dab930c10f3a9f5a2f140a51a1d1cb383a255d5e","tid":1333260,"uid":241066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:09:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24cb9c7e73f3d25a92d3aa9d266a83c2488b9cbb","tid":1333260,"uid":241066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T19:10:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba805b15dcb11df258cdda05762ec852273950db","tid":1333260,"uid":141310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"be57aac0fed538fc2d891465b352996706578035","tid":1333260,"uid":241066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:37:52.000Z","msg":"推多一次先，之後遊完行先推"},{"pid":"184d6a47f8f21b24d34cd23c85005675239f3587","tid":1333260,"uid":241066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:38:07.000Z","msg":"各位721，不見不散"},{"pid":"92d1e48ccffef910375b5f6c840f7534750c7bae","tid":1333260,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:44:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}